pr_body:
Closes #2060 This PR adds one new pgRouting function: - ``pgr_edgeColoring``: Returns the edge coloring of an undirected and loop-free (i.e *no self-loops and no parallel edges*) graph. This is a final merge PR containing commits from several different PRs combined. The intermediate PRs made on the [GSoC-pgRouting](https://github.com/pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting/) repository are as follows: | Description | Pull Requests | | -----------| --------------------- | | pgr_edgeColoring |
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#169
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#171
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#173
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#176
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#179
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#182
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#184
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#186
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#188
|

pr_body:
Closes #2060 This PR adds one new pgRouting function: - ``pgr_edgeColoring``: Returns the edge coloring of an undirected and loop-free (i.e *no self-loops and no parallel edges*) graph. This is a final merge PR containing commits from several different PRs combined. The intermediate PRs made on the [GSoC-pgRouting](https://github.com/pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting/) repository are as follows: | Description | Pull Requests | | -----------| --------------------- | | pgr_edgeColoring |
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#169
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#171
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#173
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#176
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#179
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#182
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#184
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#186

pr_body:
Closes #2060 This PR adds one new pgRouting function: - ``pgr_edgeColoring``: Returns the edge coloring of an undirected and loop-free (i.e *no self-loops and no parallel edges*) graph. This is a final merge PR containing commits from several different PRs combined. The intermediate PRs made on the [GSoC-pgRouting](https://github.com/pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting/) repository are as follows: | Description | Pull Requests | | -----------| --------------------- | | pgr_edgeColoring |
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#169
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#171
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#173
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#176
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#179
  • pgRouting/GSoC-pgRouting#182
